dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency ; modified reproduction of INT 140 originally published December 1972 (with new edition 1977 correct to NM 4/94) by Norway ; Norges sj√∏kartverk. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Norwegian copyright law applies. "Soundings in meters." Includes index to next larger scale charts. Map no.37000 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA). United States. Defense Mapping Agency. (1995). Europe, the North Sea (Raster Image). LandInfo. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/gq899rb0763 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
